FocusDeck is a study assistant app with a Flutter Web frontend and a Flask backend.
Its purpose is to allow students to:
	Generate flashcards from pasted notes
	Save flashcard sets to Firebase (via REST + ID token auth)
	Load saved flashcard sets
	Generate study guides (AI-assisted)
	Save study guides

The backend handles authentication, AI generation, and storing structured content in Firebase.
The frontend provides the UI to generate, view, save, and load flashcards/study guides.

